text: Gymnophthalmus cryptus, the cryptic spectacled tegu, is a species of lizard in the family Gymnophthalmidae. It is endemic to Venezuela. ==References== Category:Gymnophthalmus Category:Reptiles of Venezuela Category:Endemic fauna of Venezuela Category:Reptiles described in 1992 Category:Taxa named by Marinus Steven Hoogmoed Category:Taxa named by Charles J.
